International Society for Infectious Diseases
<http://www.isid.org>
[This is by no means a comprehensive collection of all reports of
dengue in the world since the last weekly update. In order to make it
more inclusive, ProMED-mail asks readers to send reports of dengue
outbreaks that they find to <promed@promedmail.org>]
In this update:
[1] Bangladesh
